org.apache.lucene.geo3d

Class XYZBounds

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.lucene.geo3d.XYZBounds
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Bounds

    public class XYZBounds
extends Object
implements Bounds
    An object for accumulating XYZ bounds information.
    WARNING: This API is experimental and might change in incompatible ways in the next release.

    • Field Detail

      • FUDGE_FACTOR

        protected static final double FUDGE_FACTOR
        A 'fudge factor', which is added to maximums and subtracted from minimums, in order to compensate for potential error deltas. This would not be necessary except that our 'bounds' is defined as always equaling or exceeding the boundary of the shape, and we cannot guarantee that without making MINIMUM_RESOLUTION unacceptably large.
        See Also:
